review_blob: Nearly black with a light brown creamy head. Nice espresso aroma with dark chocolade and honeydew melon marmelade. Heavy taste of chocolade in the begining fading to coffe and charamel. This is a beer perfect to the evening in front of the fireplace in combination with chocolade or cheese.
Fresh, tasty and good to the Swedish food.
Light burned and a cooler or a drink to the food.
